      "y": 2896.290327187969,
      "width": 420.0,
      "height": 232.0,
      "z_value": -9.754000000000136,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "label": "`#d2d1cf` \u2014 that's `(210, 209, 207)`. Let me write a batch script that reads every generated `.ico`, recolors all non-transparent pixels to that ivory while preserving alpha, and re-saves.",
      "depth_front": false,
      "node_tint": ""
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "claude_response",
      "title": "Response",
      "uuid": "95091975813c4d5faa7fed2cb48f875f",
      "x": 15170.476851660453,
      "y": -21.679417846164142,
      "width": 420.0,
      "height": 232.0,
      "z_value": -9.745000000000141,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "label": "All 23 icons rebuilt with layers up to 256px, and `iconSize` now matches `iconButtonSize` at 48px \u2014 icons fill edge to edge with no padding shrinkage. PlayStation-dominant.",
      "depth_front": false,
      "node_tint": ""
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Again he felt Shame",
      "uuid": "eb872eb651c04202b76d954a88ab00fe",
      "x": 8711.835147387555,
      "y": 7405.734151284834,
      "width": 290.19825644594766,
      "height": 216.0,
      "z_value": -9.943000000000032,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Later another group of men passed by\nPointed angrily at them saying look at this!\nIs this what you call caring these days?\nSitting on a Donkey\nLeaving a poor child running behind\n\nAgain he felt ashamed\nAnd told the boy to ride on the Donkey with him."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Gentle",
      "uuid": "bb74e092afdf41ec9aa761b80998843f",
      "x": 4615.269354102746,
      "y": 2278.9967385206255,
      "width": 301.5960665403986,
      "height": 83.54193629816473,
      "z_value": 10.0,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "And that's how we get sweetums cookies"
    },
    {
