    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Intricate",
      "uuid": "5d1ca85246b84c9faae64a1abe8463c1",
      "x": 11063.116545102426,
      "y": 7501.760613219063,
      "width": 454.4683664288025,
      "height": 136.0,
      "z_value": -9.96400000000002,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "This is really when she started changing her own approach\nNoticing how each of them took absolute command from their own peers\nWithin their relative tiers"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "claude_response",
      "title": "Response",
      "uuid": "c3ac111d137541ae94295577438b3679",
      "x": 20846.962337459758,
      "y": 2123.7089026546328,
      "width": 420.0,
      "height": 204.0,
      "z_value": -9.78300000000012,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "label": "Not in TOML yet, so it's driven purely by the Theme defaults. Two values to change \u2014 color and alpha so the hex actually renders as itself:",
      "depth_front": false,
      "node_tint": "#8a9a8a"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "image",
      "title": "Image",
      "uuid": "6fdd7d146a9d4c5e8a6090de8e253eef",
      "x": 2840.8863424052956,
      "y": -550.98316355828,
      "width": 446.90545478794274,
      "height": 657.1078318573454,
      "z_value": -9.993000000000004,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": false,
      "image_b64": "",
      "cache_key": "4aff2f99c71b9104ad579d8d4331fc32b698ba252514ff1efba64520aa8152ea",
      "caption": "HCm3ErpbQAAMQ6I",
      "source_path": "C:\\Users\\thisg\\Desktop\\_asset\\Snips\\HCm3ErpbQAAMQ6I.jpg",
      "source_size": 731909,
      "source_mtime": 1772684560.0656705,
      "show_border": true,
      "depth_front": false
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "claude_response",
      "title": "Response",
      "uuid": "599bf4dd396c44289d3ac0e6521e9216",
      "x": 22119.098896548057,
      "y": 2999.961735751941,
      "width": 420.0,
      "height": 624.0,
      "z_value": -10.0,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "label": "The criteria doc doing quiet heavy lifting every single time \u2014 \"strong clear silhouette, warm cream, outer ring identical\" and Pillow just executes it faithfully at 2048px without needing to be told twice. No designer, no asset pipeline, no back-and-forth. The whole thing takes about four seconds and produces a proper multi-resolution ICO that Qt resolves automatically at whatever size it needs.\n\nThe vision API seeding it the first time was the elegant part \u2014 letting the existing icons teach the recipe rather than us having to reverse-engineer what \"matches the family\" means.",
      "depth_front": false,
      "node_tint": "#c97a7a"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "about",
      "title": "What do you mean?",
      "uuid": "84cb3114b53149c492700b1ed6453e2f",
