      "label": "The button row is positioned at `r.top() + 4` by BaseNode. I can't move that for all nodes \u2014 just for ClaudeResponseNode. The cleanest approach: override `_position_buttons` in ClaudeResponseNode to push the buttons down by the emoji height, and paint the emoji in the freed-up top-left space.",
